data.name: btnImplants.SuperTooltip
data.value:
This form allows you to test modifications to existing implants to see what effect it has on the skill queue times.
The difference in time is displayed so allows you to see the benefit (or drawback) of changing implants.

data.name: btnRemap.SuperTooltip
data.value:
The Neural Remap feature allows you to see the effects on the skill queues of changing the base attributes of your characters.
The tool performs the same restrictions as in-game and provides details of the benefit (or drawback) of performing the selected remap.
